    .then(user => {
      routeConfig.navModel.setTitle(user.name);
    });
}
```

> Note:  `navigate(router)`  When one is encountered, the navigation will be cancelled and control will be passed to the navigation command. One navigation command is provided out of the box: `Redirect`.

### Child Routers

